title: BMW ISTA/P 2.53.5 Native + Expert mode
description:
BMW ISTA/P 2.53.5 Native + Expert mode
Year / Issue Date: 09/2014 
Version: 2.53.5.003 
System requirements: Windows 7, Windows 8 x32 x64. Powered by external drives HDD. 
Language: EN + DE + RU


Extras. information: 

- Set Ediabas 7.3.0 package BMW Standard Tools 2.12 
- Included in the distribution program EasyConnect x32 x64, iTool Radar x32 x64, EasyKFP, Ediabas Konfigurator 
- In the distribution included firmware ICOM 3.10.45 = 3.12.02. Added an overview of the release 2.53.5 and review I-level (level of integration) 
- Expert mode is included. Constant voltage is added. 
- Use the latest WinRar 5.11 
- Unlock the archives before unpacking
